detail_desc: Sports top in fast-drying functional fabric made partly from recycled polyester with a round neckline and short sleeves.
Round-necked T-shirts in soft cotton jersey.
Ankle-length leggings in cotton jersey with an elasticated waist and print motifs.
Long cardigan in a soft, fluffy knit with dropped shoulders, long sleeves and a detachable tie belt at the waist. Ribbing at the cuffs and hem. No buttons.
Shirt in a woven fabric with a matching tie or bow tie. Turn-down collar, chest pocket and buttons down the front and at the cuffs. Adjustable tie/bow tie with a plastic fastener.
5-pocket slim-fit jeans in washed, superstretch denim with an adjustable elasticated waist (in sizes 8x-12xY), zip fly and skinny legs.
Patterned swim shorts with an elasticated drawstring waist and fake fly. Soft mesh inner shorts.

Set with a T-shirt, pair of shorts and sun hat in soft cotton jersey. T-shirt that is slightly longer and rounded at the back. Shorts with an elasticated waist and sewn-in turn-ups at the hems. Lined sun hat with ties under the chin.
Long-sleeved cardigan in a soft, loose-knit viscose blend. No fasteners.
Long, thick socks in a jacquard knit with a pile lining.
V-neck top in a crêpe weave with a bead-embroidered front and narrow, adjustable shoulder straps. Lined.
Wide top in sweatshirt fabric with a lined drawstring hood, kangaroo pocket and ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
Baby Exclusive Top in organic cotton sweatshirt fabric with press-studs at the neck and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Cotton hairbands with a bow at the front and covered elastic at the back.
Comfort blanket in soft velour and jersey with an animal-shaped head and paws. Polyester filling.
Long-sleeved top in sweatshirt fabric with a lined drawstring hood and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
High-waisted, slim-fit trousers in a stretch weave with a brushed finish. Adjustable elasticated waist (in sizes 8-12Y), zip fly and button, back pockets and legs with narrow hems.
Long-sleeved tops in soft jersey made from an organic cotton blend.
Fitted top in soft organic cotton jersey with short sleeves.
Fine-knit trainer socks in a soft cotton blend with elasticated tops.
Hat and scarf set in a soft rib knit. Hat with a turned-up hem. Size of scarf 25x175 cm.
Wide T-shirt in striped jersey made from a cotton blend with gently dropped shoulders and a rounded hem.

Long, sleeveless dress in an airy, patterned jacquard weave. Narrow cut at the top with an elasticated neckline and short shoulder straps with a sewn-on bow at one side. Narrow elasticated seam at the waist. Satin lining.
Cropped top in a crinkled weave with a V-neck, lace details, narrow adjustable shoulder straps, buttons down the front and a tie-front hem.
Thong briefs in cotton jersey with lace details, a low waist and lined gusset.
Long-sleeved tops in soft jersey made from a modal and cotton blend.
Long-sleeved shirt in woven fabric with a turn-down collar, buttons down the front and at the cuffs, and a rounded hem. Easy-iron finish.
Metal hair clips decorated with plastic beads. Length 7cm and 8 cm.
Top in lightweight cotton sweatshirt fabric with a jersey-lined, wrapover hood, long raglan sleeves and ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
Pull-on trousers in woven fabric with an elasticated drawstring waist, side pockets and wide legs with contrasting colour stripes down the sides.
Double-layered hat in a soft, fine knit with an appliqué on the turned-up hem.
Ballet pumps in imitation suede with a bow at the front and grosgrain trim around the edge. Satin linings and insoles and thermoplastic rubber (TPR) soles.
Soft, non-wired lace bras in lace with mesh-lined cups with removable inserts. Narrow adjustable shoulder straps, elastication under the bust and a wide lace hem. No fasteners.
Top in soft, printed sweatshirt fabric with long sleeves, a double-layered drawstring hood with a wrapover front, a kangaroo pocket and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Calf-length skirt in soft, gently draping satin. High waist with concealed elastication and a flare to the hem. Unlined.
Jeggings in washed, superstretch denim with a high waist, fake front pockets, real back pockets and skinny legs.
Fitted, knee-length dress in soft velour with a draped neckline, 3/4-length sleeves and a seam at the waist.
Dungaree dress in washed denim with hard-worn details and adjustable straps with metal fasteners. Chest pocket, front and back pockets, and buttons at the sides. Fake fly and a raw-edge, frayed hem.
A-line skirt in slightly stretchy denim with side pockets and metal buttons down the front.
Fine-knit tights in a soft cotton blend with an elasticated waist.
Sports bra in fast-drying functional fabric with a lined front, racer back with sections in ventilating mesh and a wide elastic hem. Medium support.
Short dress in airy chiffon with a V-neck and wrapover front with ties at the waist. Long sleeves with narrow, buttoned cuffs. Pleated cuffs and a pleated skirt. Partly lined.
Trousers in cotton twill with a zip fly, side pockets, fake back pockets and a fabric belt with imitation leather details and metal D-rings.
Jazz trousers in ribbed jersey with a slight sheen. High waist with concealed elastication, and straight-cut legs with flared hems.
Short dress in soft slub jersey made from a modal and cotton blend with a slightly wider neckline, short sleeves with sewn-in turn-ups, and short slits in the sides. Unlined.
Jacket in washed, stretch denim with hard-worn details. Collar, buttons down the front, fake flap chest pockets with a button, and buttoned cuffs.
STUDIO COLLECTION. T-shirt in ribbed, cotton-blend jersey with ribbing around the neckline.
Hairband in woven fabric with a decorative knot at the front and covered elastic at the back.
Football shirt in fast-drying functional fabric with a print motif front and back. Short raglan sleeves ending in a double layer in a contrasting colour.
Wide top in a soft weave with a wide neckline with narrow elastication at the top and long, flared sleeves with smock details.
Metal chain necklace with a plastic pendant.
Trousers in soft twill with a regular, elasticated drawstring waist, side pockets, fake welt back pockets and tapered legs with slits at the hems.
Pyjamas in soft, patterned cotton jersey. Top with long sleeves and ribbed cuffs. Bottoms with an elasticated waist and ribbed hems.
Pyjamas in soft, patterned cotton jersey. Top with short, flounced sleeves. Shorts with an elasticated waist and gathered frills at the hems.
Body in jersey crêpe with an open the back and straps that cross and tie at the back. Concealed press-studs at the crotch. Unlined.
Straight-cut, knee-length dress in pleated jersey with a metallic print. Unlined.
Metal hair grips decorated with plastic rhinestones.
Calf-length dress in soft cotton jersey with a round neckline and short sleeves. Elasticated seam and a detachable tie belt at the waist and a wrapover skirt. Unlined.
Short 5-pocket skirt in washed stretch denim with a zip fly and button.
Swim pants and a swim top in UV-protective fabric. Print-patterned top with long raglan sleeves. Bottoms with a frill at the top and lined gusset. UPF 50.
V-neck jersey T-shirt in a stretch cotton blend. Slim fit.
Bracelets in fabric and metal with decorative shells.
5-pocket trousers in washed, slightly stretchy twill with a regular waist, zip fly and skinny legs. Skinny fit.
A-line dress in a crinkled, patterned weave with hemstitch details, a round neck and opening with buttons at the back. Long trumpet sleeves with crochet lace trims. Unlined.
Padded earmuffs in faux fur with a soft fleece inside. Adjustable headband in shimmering imitation leather.
Joggers in lightweight sweatshirt fabric with an elasticated drawstring waist, low crotch, side pockets and ribbed hems. Soft brushed inside.
Boxy-style jumper in a fine knit with a soft, brushed finish. Low dropped shoulders and long dolman sleeves.
Wide Alice band covered in braided satin ribbon. Width approx. 3.5 cm.
Straight-cut, V-neck blouse in a cotton weave with large frills at the top and concealed buttons down the front. Long, wide sleeves with pleats and buttons at the cuffs.
Long-sleeved top in sweatshirt fabric made from a cotton blend. Lined hood with a wrapover front, and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Slim-fit, high-waisted jeans in washed, superstretch denim. Adjustable, elasticated waist (in sizes 8-12Y), zip fly, fake front pockets, real back pockets and narrow, raw-edge hems.
Fine-knit jumper in a modal and cotton blend with a ribbed turtle neck and long sleeves.

Baby Exclusive. Short-sleeved bodysuits in soft, organic cotton pointelle jersey with a V-neck and button placket. Decorative picot trim around the neckline, sleeves and legs, and press-studs at the crotch.
Cropped top in ribbed jersey with a deep round neckline, decorative buttons down the front and short sleeves. The cotton content of the top is organic.
Longer-style jacket in woven fabric with notch lapels and welt front pockets with a flap. Lined.

Jacket in woven fabric with heat-pressed quilting and a filling of 80% down and 20% feathers. Lined hood with an elastic drawstring, a zip down the front, side pockets and an inner pocket. Inner ribbing at the cuffs and a concealed elastic drawstring at the hem. Lined.
Fitted, sleeveless, calf-length dress in soft, ribbed jersey made from a cotton blend with high slits in the sides.
Sandals in imitation leather and fabric with a heel strap and a hook and loop fastening at one side. Imitation leather insoles and rubber soles.
Short, sleeveless dress in glittery jersey with a V-neck and narrow shoulder straps. Unlined.
Thong briefs in lace with a low waist, scalloped edges at the front, lined gusset and string back.
